<item>
  <title><![CDATA[Record My Gentoo Linux Install]]></title>
  <description><![CDATA[

<div id="outline-container-org21a8f52" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org21a8f52"><span class="todo TODO">TODO</span> Incomplete</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org21a8f52">
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>boot partition not in zpool and not encryption</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org0da9749" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org0da9749">LiveCD</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org0da9749">
<p>
For zfs installation, I need <a href="https://github.com/nchevsky/systemrescue-zfs">systemrescue-zfs</a> or <a href="https://gitlab.com/m_zhou/archiso">archiso</a>.
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orge60ce58" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="orge60ce58">Format and Partition</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-orge60ce58">
<p>
My normal GPT partition plan:
</p>
<table>


<colgroup>
<col  class="org-left">

<col  class="org-left">

<col  class="org-left">
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td class="org-left">Device</td>
<td class="org-left">Size</td>
<td class="org-left">Type</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td class="org-left">/dev/nvme0n1p1</td>
<td class="org-left">80M</td>
<td class="org-left">EFI System</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td class="org-left">/dev/nvme0n1p2</td>
<td class="org-left">Memory Size</td>
<td class="org-left">Linux swap</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td class="org-left">/dev/nvme0n1p3</td>
<td class="org-left">All Other Size</td>
<td class="org-left">Linux filesystem</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-shell">fdisk /dev/nvme0n1 
</pre>
</div>
<p>
Let me format the partitions:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-shell">mkfs.fat -F32 /dev/nvme0n1p1
mkswap -f /dev/nvme0n1p2
swapon /dev/nvme0n1p2
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgfdee859" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="orgfdee859">Create zpool</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-orgfdee859">
<p>
Use native encryption and zstd compression:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-shell">zpool create -f -O encryption=on -O keyformat=passphrase -o ashift=12 -o cachefile= -O compression=zstd -O acltype=posixacl -O atime=off -O xattr=sa -m none -R /mnt/gentoo kpool /dev/disk/by-id/nvme-xxx-part2 
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orge6ea1eb" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="orge6ea1eb">Create zfs datasets</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-orge6ea1eb">
<p>
Just create root and home datasets:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-shell">zfs create kpool/gentoo
zfs create -o mountpoint=/ kpool/gentoo/os
zfs create -o mountpoint=/home kpool/gentoo/home
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org94f187e" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org94f187e">Install stage3</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org94f187e">
<p>
Go gentoo website:<a href="https://bouncer.gentoo.org/fetch/root/all/releases/amd64/autobuilds/current-stage3-amd64/">Stage3</a>, Normal I use stage3-amd64-nomultilib:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-shell">cd /mnt/gentoo
wget ......
tar vxpf stage3-*.tar.xz --xattrs-include=<span style="color: #8b0000;">'*.*'</span> --numeric-owner
rm stage*
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orga3fa163" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="orga3fa163">Mount partition</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-orga3fa163">
<p>
For zfs, I only mount one partition:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-shell">mount /dev/nvme0n1p1 /mnt/gentoo/boot
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org1614eb2" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org1614eb2">Generate fstab</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org1614eb2">
<p>
Normal, I use archiso, the fstab file only one command:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-shell">genfstab -U /mnt/gentoo &gt; /mnt/gentoo/etc/fstab
</pre>
</div>
<p>
Delete no use mountpoint:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-shell">nano /mnt/gentoo/etc/fstab 
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org1ac8173" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org1ac8173">Edit /etc/portage/make.conf</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org1ac8173">
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-shell">nano /mnt/gentoo/etc/portage/make.conf
</pre>
</div>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-conf"><span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;"># </span><span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;">GCC</span>
CFLAGS=<span style="color: #8b0000;">"-march=native -O3 -pipe"</span>
CXXFLAGS=<span style="color: #8b0000;">"${CFLAGS}"</span>
CHOST=<span style="color: #8b0000;">"x86_64-pc-linux-gnu"</span>
<span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;"># </span><span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;">3600</span>
CPU_FLAGS_X86=<span style="color: #8b0000;">"aes avx avx2 f16c fma3 mmx mmxext pclmul popcnt rdrand sha sse sse2 sse3 sse4_1 sse4_2 sse4a ssse3"</span>
<span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;"># </span><span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;">Surface GO</span>
<span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;"># </span><span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;">CPU_FLAGS_X86="aes mmx mmxext pclmul popcnt rdrand sse sse2 sse3 sse4_1 sse4_2 ssse3"</span>
<span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;"># </span><span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;">Nas</span>
<span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;"># </span><span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;">CPU_FLAGS_X86="mmx mmxext pclmul popcnt rdrand sse sse2 sse3 sse4_1 sse4_2 ssse3"</span>
<span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;"># </span><span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;">MAKEOPTS="-j5"</span>
MAKEOPTS=<span style="color: #8b0000;">"-j13"</span>

<span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;"># </span><span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;">USE</span>
USE=<span style="color: #8b0000;">"-bindist elogind gtk pulseaudio -consolekit -systemd -clang"</span>

<span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;"># </span><span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;">Portage</span>
<span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;"># </span><span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;">GENTOO_MIRRORS="https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/gentoo/"</span>
EMERGE_DEFAULT_OPTS=<span style="color: #8b0000;">"--ask --verbose=y --keep-going --with-bdeps=y --load-average"</span>
<span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;"># </span><span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;">FEATURES="${FEATURES} -userpriv -usersandbox -sandbox"</span>
ACCEPT_KEYWORDS=<span style="color: #8b0000;">"~amd64"</span>
ACCEPT_LICENSE=<span style="color: #8b0000;">"*"</span>

<span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;"># </span><span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;">Language</span>
L10N=<span style="color: #8b0000;">"en-US zh-CN en zh"</span>
LINGUAS=<span style="color: #8b0000;">"en_US zh_CN en zh"</span>

<span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;"># </span><span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;">Else</span>
<span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;"># </span><span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;">VIDEO_CARDS="intel i965"</span>
VIDEO_CARDS=<span style="color: #8b0000;">"amdgpu radeonsi"</span>
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org359a7f4" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org359a7f4">Configure portage repos</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org359a7f4">
<p>
I use git:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-shell">mkdir /mnt/gentoo/etc/portage/repos.conf
nano /mnt/gentoo/etc/portage/repos.conf/gentoo.conf
</pre>
</div>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-conf">[DEFAULT]
main-repo = gentoo

[gentoo]
location = /var/db/repos/gentoo
sync-type = git
sync-uri = https://github.com/gentoo-mirror/gentoo
auto-sync = yes
</pre>
</div>
<p>
Clone portage repo:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-shell">git clone --depth=1 https://github.com/gentoo-mirror/gentoo /mnt/gentoo/var/db/repos/gentoo
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgfa9e235" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="orgfa9e235">Copy zpool cachefile</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-orgfa9e235">
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-shell">mkdir /mnt/gentoo/etc/zfs
cp /etc/zfs/zpool.cache /mnt/gentoo/etc/zfs
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org70c4214" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org70c4214">Now chroot</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org70c4214">
<p>
Let me chroot:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-shell"><span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;"># </span><span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;">dns</span>
cp --dereference /etc/resolv.conf /mnt/gentoo/etc/
<span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;"># </span><span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;">mount</span>
mount -t proc none proc
mount --rbind /sys sys
mount --rbind /dev dev
<span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;"># </span><span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;">chroot</span>
chroot /mnt/gentoo /bin/bash
source /etc/profile
export PS1=<span style="color: #8b0000;">"(chroot) ${PS1}"</span>  
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org0629583" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org0629583">Configure current system</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org0629583">
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-shell"><span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;"># </span><span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;">check profile is correct</span>
eselect profile list
<span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;"># </span><span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;">if not correct</span>
eselect profile set x
<span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;"># </span><span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;">timezone</span>
echo <span style="color: #8b0000;">"Asia/Shanghai"</span> &gt; /etc/timezone
emerge --config sys-libs/timezone-data
<span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;"># </span><span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;">locale</span>
echo <span style="color: #8b0000;">"en_US.UTF-8 UTF-8</span>
<span style="color: #8b0000;">zh_CN.UTF-8 UTF-8"</span> &gt;&gt; /etc/locale.gen
locale-gen
eselect locale list
eselect locale set
<span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;"># </span><span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;">hostname</span>
echo hostname=<span style="color: #8b0000;">\"</span>MyHostName<span style="color: #8b0000;">\"</span> &gt; /etc/conf.d/hostname
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orga67a066" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="orga67a066">Compile the world</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-orga67a066">
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-shell">emerge -vDuUq @world
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgfc9bc7e" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="orgfc9bc7e">Compile kernel</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-orgfc9bc7e">
<p>
I have .config file:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-shell">cd /usr/src/linux
cp /path/to/.config .
make -j13
make install
make modules_install
</pre>
</div>
<p>
I don't have .config file:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-shell">cd /usr/src/linux
make localmodconfig
make -j13
make install
make modules_install
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgace7709" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="orgace7709">Install zfs</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-orgace7709">
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-shell">emerge zfs
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org6c24a4d" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org6c24a4d">Generate initramfs</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org6c24a4d">
<p>
I use dracut:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-shell"><span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;"># </span><span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;">don't need resume</span>
dracut -H --kver xx
<span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;"># </span><span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;">need resume</span>
dracut -a <span style="color: #8b0000;">"resume"</span> -H --kver xx
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org15d1915" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org15d1915">Add OpenRC service to boot or default</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org15d1915">
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-shell">rc-update add zfs-import boot
rc-update add zfs-mount boot
rc-update add elogind boot
rc-update add sshd
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org6a51254" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org6a51254">User manager</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org6a51254">
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-shell">passwd
useradd -m -G users,wheel,portage,usb,video xx
passwd xx
<span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;"># </span><span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;">sudo</span>
sed -i <span style="color: #8b0000;">'s/\# \%wheel ALL=(ALL) ALL/\%wheel ALL=(ALL) ALL/g'</span> /etc/sudoers
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org061d069" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org061d069">Configure Bootloader</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org061d069">
<p>
I use systemd-boot:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-shell"><span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;"># </span><span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;">install</span>
bootctl install --path /boot
</pre>
</div>
<p>
edit loader file
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-shell">nano /boot/loader/loader.conf
</pre>
</div>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-conf">default gentoo.conf
timeout 2
editor 0
</pre>
</div>
<p>
edit entries file
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-shell">nano /boot/loader/entries/gentoo.conf
</pre>
</div>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-conf"><span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;"># </span><span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;">normal</span>
title   Gentoo Linux
linux   /vmlinuz-xx-gentoo
initrd  /initramfs-xx-gentoo.img
options root=ZFS=kpool/gentoo/os rw spl.spl_hostid=0x00bab10c resume=UUID=swap uuid
<span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;"># </span><span style="color: #006400; font-style: italic;">amd pci passthrough</span>
title   Gentoo Linux With GPU
linux   /vmlinuz-xx-gentoo
initrd  /initramfs-xx-gentoo.img
options root=ZFS=kpool/gentoo/os rw spl.spl_hostid=0x00bab10c amd_iommu=on iommu=pt pcie_acs_override=downstream,multifunction vfio_iommu_type1.allow_unsafe_interrupts=1
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org1e5c252" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org1e5c252">Umount and export zpool</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org1e5c252">
<p>
The end step:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-shell">umount /boot/
swapooff /dev/nvme0n1p2
<span style="color: #00008b;">exit</span>
umount -l sys
umount -l proc
umount -l dev
cd /
zpool export kpool
poweroff
</pre>
</div>
<p>
Happy Enjoy The New System.
</p>
</div>
</div>
